//No what are we doing wasting time here supposed to be on a journey lets get this over with I will burn these ships down if you keep playing games
text MareS9_Text_Beroe_Funeral2 {
    format("We did not cross the unforgiving seas,
			navigate Scylla Charybdis, escape
			Isla Solata, or sacrifice the
			flower of our youth for you to play games
			on some savage island! Have you forgot
			the prophesy Kassandra told of you?
			Mighty Aeneas, father of the kings
			who one day will rule all the world from the
			great city you are destined to create,
			let not those hero's deaths have been in vain.
			We should set sail while the winds favor us,
			while we still have our strenghth, and while our ship,
			freshly repaired, is eager for the surf.")
}

